{"type": "article", "id": 23933, "title": "装相机的背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 170, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154118BRVh1fOGXtAqixzm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款背包有强大的装相机的空间，它有像格子一样的划分可装一个完整的单反和 3 到 5 个镜头，背包里也可以放 13 寸到 15 寸的电脑。它使用了有一定防水作用的纺织物，在扣子和一些点缀的细节处用了皮革，有提亮的功能。可以选择军绿色、灰色和黑色三种。目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/vinta/s-series-travel-and-camera-bag\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154116FkrzO0SxABDYCfXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215411603uJ6hXiRMwyTQ7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154117xPT7RNB3UMGqFiJl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154117clXPz0ET13BQtnIq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}